Jay Harrington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jay_Harrington 0 James H. Harrington III, professionally known as Jay Harrington, (born November 15, 1971) is an American actor. He is known for his role as the title character in the ABC sitcom Better Off Ted and as Deacon Kay in S.W.A.T.
